This release contains several bugfixes and new functionality.

- Updated screen of the Sales Order document - sales tax and price are recalculated in lines when a customer or an address is changed in the document;
- Improved CSV Data Import - improved performance and more uploading fields for the Customer/Vendor import function;
- Period closing functionality;
- Addresses now have ﬁve user-deﬁned custom ﬁelds allowing you to tailor the software according to your speciﬁc business needs;
- Improvements in the bank reconciliation module: ability to reclass transactions that are already included in the bank reconciliation. Improved UX in the bank reconciliation document - reconcile all, sorting by every column, totals by receipts and payments, linking to Downloaded Transactions;
- Added matching to the Deposit document in the Downloaded Transactions module.
